Routh is now expected to be charged with capital murder over the double shooting.

Erath County Sheriff Tommy Bryant said that he had ‘no clue’ as to the motive but US reports focused on Routh’s PTSD.

In interviews Kyle himself has told of how hard it is to leave the military and said it left you with ‘no identity’.

He left the service in 2009 in order to save his marriage to wife Taya and spend more time with their two children.

